OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright, breezy day with some
OL,6,Fsunny intervals. Most places will be
OL,7,Fdry, but the odd light shower in the
OL,8,Fnorth can't be ruled out.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FLargely dry in the evening
OL,11,Fwith bright then clear spells and
OL,12,Fvariable cloud. Mostly dry overnight
OL,13,Fbut turning cloudier. Small chance of
OL,14,Fthe odd light shower.
OL,15,
OL,16,CFriday:FDry with variable cloud and
OL,17,Fbright spells through the morning.
OL,18,FSome rain spreads east through the
OL,19,Fafternoon, perhaps heavy at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
